# Chillax ğŸ’¤

**Chillax** is not just another wrapper â€” itâ€™s a whole new way of coding with AI.  
Instead of memorizing a fixed set of functions, **you decide what functions you want**.  
Every function you call on `Chillax` gets passed straight to AI â€” so you can literally invent your own function names on the fly and theyâ€™ll just work. (vibecoding supremacy)

