## ğŸš€ Features

- **One-line setup** â†’ just set your API key and youâ€™re ready to go  
- **Make up your own functions** â†’ `chillax.sort()`, `chillax.translate()`, `chillax.summarize()`, `chillax.reverse()`, `chillax.doMagicTrick()` â€¦ literally any name you choose will work  
- **Lightweight & beginner-friendly** â†’ no heavy dependencies, perfect for vibecoders who want to focus on coding instead of setup  

